dct_title_s: Automobile touring route from Los Angeles through San Fernando Valley and return
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Oriented with north toward upper right.
Shows city plans, roads, railroads, waterways.
Numbered 60 in lower left and 19 in bottom margin.
Belongs to a series of strip maps showing roads in California.
